				<td colspan="2"><span>While I certainly don't encourage training people or causing other things to happen that will get them killed, if you were to train the cleric, bard, or try to screw up the macro by rooting or in some other way, it's highly doubtful you would get banned.  For one, the guy afk macroing would not even be able to petition you until it's too late (and even then he most likely wouldn't know who did it, you don't have to fade to train mobs on someone in PoN (learned that the hard way training stalkers onto my wife when swarming, oops :p)).  Even if he did know your name and petitioned you, they won't be able to prove it was intentional and unless you get petitioned for that a lot, I doubt they'll take action.  
