				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Bard xp bot  &amp;gt;&amp;lt;<a name="42142"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 25 04 3:21 PM</span></td>
